make an app to order online driver 
requirement :
- 10000 every km
- 5% disc when over 50km
- 10% disc when over 100km
- 20% when user order over 2x
- 30% when oreder over 5x  with 10% tax

How to do:
- data can be saved into database with username as user
- when user order, save data into transaction
- record every order on transaction table

Initialization:
- init nodejs
- install nodeenv
- install knex for db ORM

